('msg-122', 'conv-018', 'assistant', 'Management plan documented for Fatima Begum: Start MNT with dietitian referral, SMBG 4 times daily, and review in 2 weeks. If targets not met, initiate Metformin 500mg BD. Delivery plan: Target 38-39 weeks with continuous fetal monitoring. Postpartum: OGTT at 6 weeks post-delivery to screen for Type 2 DM.', 'text', NULL, '2026-03-26 14:30:00'),
